description: |
  Adding new option of tmt command, ``--allowed-runner-devices``, and a
  corresponding environment variable, ``TMT_ALLOWED_RUNNER_DEVICES``.
  When a guest asks for a runner device to be exposed to said guest, e.g.
  via podman's ``--device`` option or as a libvirt "node device", only
  the devices whose path matches any of the regular expressions passed
  to the option would be exposed to said guest.
